acdecom.WaveGuide.find_cuton¶

WaveGuide.find_cuton(self, f, **kwargs)¶

Returns the number of cut-on modes for the specified frequency f Hz.

Parameters

  • f (float) – Frequency in Hz.

  • kwargs (additional arguments) –

Returns

Number of cut-on modes. Symmetric modes are counted as two modes, i.e., after the first cut-on in a circular duct, three modes can propagate.

Return type

int
